The paper focuses on the physical layer security of millimeter wave ad hoc networks, which involves the study of information theory, networking, and security. Therefore, cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also specifically mentions millimeter wave networks, which falls under the sub-category cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper proposes a tractable approach to evaluate the average achievable secrecy rate, which involves system modeling and analysis, and thus falls under the sub-category cs.SY (Systems and Control).
